title: Twisted Treeline Queue Time Live?  (ranked) :)
body: Hi I was just wondering what time NZT or AEST 3v3/twisted treeline comes live? I've been playing it the last few days in a row and I've been having an absolute blast. Would love to know when it comes live and on what days :) thankyou!!
